strings: <voice_0x0100176B><se_low>*: Welcome to the race. Our dragons come in two forms<:> Human and Dragon.
<voice_0x0100176C><se_low>*: I am Chen Mui, the eldest of Dragovia. I am your guide
<voice_0x0100176D><se_low>jungmi: The last time humans entered the Sanctuary was hundreds of years ago.
<voice_0x0100176E><se_low>jungmi: Some dragons may be surprised by your sudden appearance. That's why I have to stay with you.
<voice_0x0100176F><se_low>jungmi: Understand that the attendant may feel uncomfortable.
